entry.title: They Believe Pesticides Caused Their Cancers. Proving It Is Almost Impossible.
entry.content: Farmworkers in California’s Salinas Valley work with pesticides tied to illnesses, including some cancers.

entry.title: Brazen Burglars Are Crashing Vehicles Into Stores
entry.content: In a tactic called “ram raiding,” burglars drive a stolen vehicle through a storefront and then loot ATMs, guns and other valuables inside.
